metadata.name: Gallant Rooster
metadata.description:
This piece was created in collaboration with AI, drawing upon the rich visual and narrative traditions of the medieval era to explore the realm of fantasy. 

Inspired by Tim Ferris' Cockpunch world, the piece was crafted to capture the fantastical world that I had imagined as I immersed myself in the narrative. Using advanced technology and referencing the medieval aesthetic, we were able to bring my vision to life in a way that is true to its inspiration and uniquely our own.
